8260	\begin{lemma}[Nested coproducts flatten to a coproduct over pairs]
8261	  \label{lem:sigmaSigmaIso_mathlib}
8262	  \lean{CategoryTheory.Limits.sigmaSigmaIso}
8263	  \mathlibok
8264	  \textit{Provided by Mathlib.}
8265	  For a doubly-indexed family \((Z_{i,j})\), the nested coproduct is the coproduct over pairs:
